WhitelistTokenTest
├── When caller is not Admin
│   └── It should revert with NotAdmin
└── When caller is Admin
    ├── When token to whitelist is the Zero Address
    │   └── It should revert with ZeroAddress
    └── When token to whitelist is not the Zero Address
        ├── When whitelist state is true
        │   ├── It should set the token's whitelist state to true
        │   └── It should emit a {WhitelistToken} event
        └── When whitelist state is false
            ├── It should set the token's whitelist state to false
            └── It should emit a {WhitelistToken} event
